<template>
    <tbody>
        <!-- <MisaTableBodyTr :colum="colum" :scroll="scroll" @show="onClickDetail(item)" v-for="item in datas" :key="item" @dblclick="onClickDetail(item)" :datas="item"></MisaTableBodyTr> -->
    </tbody>
</template>

<script>
// import router from '@/router/router'
import MisaTableBodyTr from './MisaTableBodyTr.vue';

export default {
    name: "MisaTableBody",
    props: {
        datas: {
            type: Array,
            // default:[["test","test","test","test","test",true]],
        },
        scroll:{
            type:Number,
            default:0
        },
        colum:{
            type:[]  
        }
    },
    components: { MisaTableBodyTr },
    data() {
        return {
            hasfuntion: false,
        }
    },
    methods: {
        /**
         * Truyền dữ liệu lên from
         * Auther: Nguyễn Quân
         * Created:05/2023 
         */
        onClickDetail(item) {
            this.$emit("showPopup",item.id)
        },
    },
}
</script>

<style></style>
